"{\"uid\": \"dailyhive.com-vancouver-vancouver-olympic-village-elementary-school-funding-update\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Urbanized van No capital funding for the construction of thelong-envisioned new Olympic Village elementary schoolwas included in the2024 provincial budget announced today.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Urbanized van No capital funding\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 32}, {\"ngram\": \"the construction\", \"from\": 37, \"to\": 53}, {\"ngram\": \"the2024 provincial budget\", \"from\": 129, \"to\": 154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when asked during a closed session for media, BC Minister of Finance Katrine Conway quipped that an announcement would be forthcoming in the \\\"coming weeks.\\\"\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 225, \"end\": 227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.021791780059576e-20, \"text\": \"BC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia\"}, {\"begin\": 256, \"end\": 262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\", \"score\": 0.9920695298827724, \"rank\": 0.007993865226725313, \"text\": \"Conway\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a closed session\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 213}, {\"ngram\": \"media\", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 223}, {\"ngram\": \"an announcement\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 291}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"coming weeks\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An elementary school serving the growing high-density residential neighbourhood in Vancouver's Southeast False Creek area has been planned by the municipal government since the 2000s.\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 420, \"end\": 429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2996484119493963e-16, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An elementary school\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"the growing high-density residential neighbourhood\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"the municipal government\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In more recent years,municipal officials, residents in the area, andparents of nearby schools experiencing long waitlists at their at-capacity catchment schoolhave been calling for the provincial government to expedite funding for the project.\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more recent years\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"municipal officials\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 561}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 584}, {\"ngram\": \"andparents\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"nearby schools\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"long waitlists\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 642}, {\"ngram\": \"-capacity\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 663}, {\"ngram\": \"the provincial government\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"funding\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"the project\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BC NDP included an Olympic Village elementary school as acampaign promise in the 2020 election, and the last formal update provided on the project was inJune 2022, when the BC Ministry of Education and Child Care provided the concept plan with preliminary approval, enabling Vancouver School Board to enter the next stage of planning.\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 1104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Columbia_New_Democratic_Party\", \"score\