es ahead of the general provincial election later in 2024.\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A forthcoming funding announcement\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"this project\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"the general provincial election\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In accordance with the City of Vancouver's Southeast False Creek Plan, the new school will be located on a temporary open grassy parcel on the east side of Hinge Park - the parcel at the southwest corner of the intersection of Athletes Way and Columbia Street, next to the seawall.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"accordance\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"Vancouver's Southeast False Creek Plan\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"the new school\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"a temporary open grassy parcel\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"the east side\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"Hinge Park\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"the parcel\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"the southwest corner\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"the intersection\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"Athletes Way and Columbia Street\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"the seawall\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, VSB and Vancouver City Council approved a 99-year lease for the use of the City-owned site for an elementary school.\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1526, \"end\": 1535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2996484119493963e-16, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}, {\"begin\": 1526, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_City_Council\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vancouver City Council\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_City_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_City_Council\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"VSB\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"a 99-year lease\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"the City-owned site\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"an elementary school\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vancouver City Council and the Vancouver School Board (VSB) announced today they have approved entering into a 99-year lease for the school site.\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1636, \"end\": 1658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_City_Council\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vancouver City Council\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_City_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_City_Council\"}, {\"begin\": 1636, \"end\": 1645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2996484119493963e-16, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}, {\"begin\": 1667, \"end\": 1689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_School_Board\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vancouver School Board\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_School_Board\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver_School_Board\"}, {\"begin\": 1667, \"end\": 1676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\",