 school and daycare.\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2087, \"end\": 2096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2996484119493963e-16, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}, {\"begin\": 2099, \"end\": 2114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999886690604, \"rank\": 1.1330750225352747e-08, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(City\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2027}, {\"ngram\": \"Vancouver\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"The large open grassy site\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2068}, {\"ngram\": \"Hinge Park\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2082}, {\"ngram\": \"an elementary school\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"daycare\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Kenneth Chan/Daily Hive) Based on a previous VSB facilities plan, this Kindergarten to Grade 7 school could have a capacity for over 500 students and incorporate a childcare facility, with an elementary school and childcare facility co-location increasingly common for new build projects.\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2170, \"end\": 2182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenneth_Chan_Kai-tai\", \"score\": 0.8253855353336108, \"rank\": 0.21155503360740105, \"text\": \"Kenneth Chan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenneth_Chan_Kai-tai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenneth_Chan_Kai-tai\"}, {\"begin\": 2183, \"end\": 2193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Hive\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daily Hive\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Hive\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Hive\"}, {\"begin\": 2242, \"end\": 2254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kindergarten\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.7517414288154483e-12, \"text\": \"Kindergarten\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kindergarten\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kindergarten\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a previous VSB facilities plan\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"Grade 7 school\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2271}, {\"ngram\": \"a capacity\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"over 500 students\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"a childcare facility\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"an elementary school and childcare facility co\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2405}, {\"ngram\": \"location\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2414}, {\"ngram\": \"new build projects\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Conway also faced questions about the provincial government's urgency to respond to the City of Surrey and Surrey School District's (SSD) pleas to direct more capital funding to ramp up the pace of building new permanent purpose-built structures toreplace Surrey's growing dependency on portable structures- including thefuture possibility of two-storey portable structures- and the community's continued high enrolment due to high population growth.\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2461, \"end\": 2467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\", \"score\": 0.9920695298827724, \"rank\": 0.007993865226725313, \"text\": \"Conway\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\"}, {\"begin\": 2717, \"end\": 2723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surrey\", \"score\": 0.9999999939982445, \"rank\": 4.2428076433838896e-09, \"text\": \"Surrey\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surrey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surrey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2488}, {\"ngram\": \"the provincial government's urgency\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2530}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2553}, {\"ngram\": \"Surrey\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2563}, {\"ngram\": \"Surrey School District\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2590}, {\"ngram\": \"(SSD\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"pleas\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2604}, {\"ngram\": \"more capital funding\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"the pace\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2655}, {\"ngram\": \"new permanent purpose-built structures\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2706}, {\"ngram\": \"portable structures-\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2768}, {\"ngram\": \"thefuture possibility\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2800}, {\"ngram\": \"two-storey portable structures-\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2835}, {\"ngram\": \"the community's continued high enrolment\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2880}, {\"ngram\": \"high population growth\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By the new school year starting in September 2024, there could bealmost 400 portables at public schools across Surrey.\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 3031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3024, \"end\": 3030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surrey\", \"score\": 0.9999999939982445, \"rank\": 4.2428076433838896e-09, \"text\": \"Surrey\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surrey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surrey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the new school year\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 2957}, {\"ngram\": \"400 portables\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 2998}, {\"ngram\": \"public schools\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As of 2019, about 10% of SSD's students were already in portables.\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3057, \"end\": 3060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solid-state_drive\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.7549661892096174e-30, \"text\": \"SSD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solid-state_drive\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solid-state_drive\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about 10%\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3053}, {\"ngram\": \"portables\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coincidentally, today, SSD announced it will resort to extending the school day at five of its most crowded secondary schools to address capacity challenges, including at Grandview Heights Secondary, Fleetwood Park Secondary, Lord Tweedsmuir Secondary, Kwantlen Park Secondary, and Tamanawis Secondary.\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3123, \"end\": 3126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solid-state_drive\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.7549661892096174e-30, \"text\": \"SSD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solid-state_drive\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solid-state_drive\"}, {\"begin\": 3326, \"end\": 3351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lord_Tweedsmuir_Secondary_School\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lord Tweedsmuir Secondary\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lord_Tweedsmuir_Secondary_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lord_Tweedsmuir_Secondary_School\"}, {\"begin\": 3353, \"end\": 3361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kwantlen_Polytechnic_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999316701201, \"rank\": 6.833000981933131e-08, \"text\": \"Kwantlen\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kwantlen_Polytechnic_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kwantlen_Polytechnic_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the school day\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3179}, {\"ngram\": \"its most crowded secondary schools\", \"from\": 3191, \"to\": 3225}, {\"ngram\": \"capacity challenges\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3256}, {\"ngram\": \"Grandview Heights Secondary\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3298}, {\"ngram\": \"Fleetwood Park Secondary\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3324}, {\"ngram\": \"Tamanawis Secondary\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will start in September 2024.\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 3422, \"to\": 3431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An extended school day will enable a staggered student attendance schedule to increase each school's capacity by 10% to 15%.\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3563, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An extended school day\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3461}, {\"ngram\": \"a staggered student attendance schedule\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3513}, {\"ngram\": \"each school's capacity\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3548}, {\"ngram\": \"10% to 15%\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This extended school day involves lengthening the school day by one block/class period, so there will be five blocks instead of four blocks.\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3704, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This extended school day\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3588}, {\"ngram\": \"the school day\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3624}, {\"ngram\": \"one block/class period\", \"from\": 3628, \"to\": 3650}, {\"ngram\": \"five blocks\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3680}, {\"ngram\": \"four blocks\", \"from\": 3692, \"to\": 3703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By May 2024, SSD will decide on whether it will deploy the same extended school day strategy at Fraser Heights Secondary and Salish Secondary.\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3719, \"end\": 3722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solid-state_drive\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.7549661892096174e-30, \"text\": \"SSD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solid-state_drive\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solid-state_drive\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 3709, \"to\": 3712}, {\"ngram\": \"the same extended school day strategy\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3798}, {\"ngram\": \"Fraser Heights Secondary and Salish Secondary\", \"from\": 3802, \"to\": 3847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Extended day is not an option we want to implement.\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 3902, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Extended day\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3863}, {\"ngram\": \"an option\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We know there are likely going to be challenges for our staff, our students, and their families.\", \"from\": 3903, \"to\": 3999, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"challenges\", \"from\": 3940, \"to\": 3950}, {\"ngram\": \"our staff\", \"from\": 3955, \"to\": 3964}, {\"ngram\": \"our students\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 3978}, {\"ngram\": \"their families\", \"from\": 3984, \"to\": 3998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our preference is to construct new schools and additions in neighbourhoods where they are needed, but we have to explore other options while we continue to advocate for provincial funding,\\\" said Laurie Larsen, chair of the SSD, in a statement.\", \"from\": 4000, \"to\": 4243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4223, \"end\": 4226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solid-state_drive\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.7549661892096174e-30, \"text\": \"SSD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solid-state_drive\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Solid-state_drive\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our preference\", \"from\": 4000, \"to\": 4014}, {\"ngram\": \"new schools\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4042}, {\"ngram\": \"additions\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4056}, {